What about that?

00:03:57.925 --> 00:03:59.135
Excuse me.

00:04:01.387 --> 00:04:02.513
Hello?

00:04:05.641 --> 00:04:06.601
What?

00:04:11.481 --> 00:04:12.482
Yuri…

00:04:16.444 --> 00:04:17.487
Yuri…

00:04:22.617 --> 00:04:24.327
Yuri…

