You monster!

00:04:30.917 --> 00:04:33.086
You people killed Yuri.

00:04:35.713 --> 00:04:37.548
Give me my Yuri back.

00:04:38.466 --> 00:04:39.509
Give her back.

00:04:40.009 --> 00:04:42.178
Give my Yuri back!

