00:07:50.324 --> 00:07:51.951
What is the meaning of this?

00:07:52.618 --> 00:07:54.036
Meaning of what?

00:07:54.620 --> 00:07:58.124
Why did you allow Kuryu to get the role?

00:08:02.420 --> 00:08:05.590
Why do you side with Ioka to this extent?

00:08:09.260 --> 00:08:10.928
Do you hate me that much?

00:08:11.012 --> 00:08:13.973
Don't flaunt your own pettiness!

00:08:30.906 --> 00:08:33.034
A US-Japan joint production.

00:08:33.117 --> 00:08:37.538
We'll make the announcement
after the JBS special drama conference.

00:08:37.622 --> 00:08:39.206
So it's finally time.

00:08:39.290 --> 00:08:42.835
Let's make sure
your American debut goes well.

00:08:43.794 --> 00:08:44.920
Which is why…

00:08:47.298 --> 00:08:48.382
What is it?

00:08:55.848 --> 00:08:57.475
I'm counting on you, okay?

00:08:58.142 --> 00:08:59.268
Of course.

00:09:00.144 --> 00:09:02.063
I'm very grateful to you.

00:09:02.688 --> 00:09:04.065
I'll repay the favor.

00:09:15.493 --> 00:09:17.536
Sexually assaulted by Aso?

00:09:18.871 --> 00:09:21.082
The other party came to us.

00:09:23.501 --> 00:09:27.296
It was your leadership that made
Mr. Aso into the face of your agency,

00:09:27.963 --> 00:09:31.425
which is precisely why
if people found out about this,

00:09:31.509 --> 00:09:33.969
you would be forced
to take responsibility.

00:09:37.431 --> 00:09:40.851
I expect the public
will react quite strongly,

00:09:41.435 --> 00:09:44.772
especially considering the subject matter.

00:09:54.949 --> 00:09:56.283
For next year,

00:09:56.367 --> 00:10:01.747
we'll give Buncho exclusive rights to sell
calendars featuring our idol talents.

00:10:04.250 --> 00:10:05.418
On top of that…

00:10:08.295 --> 00:10:11.006
I'm sure you need
another scoop in exchange.

00:10:18.514 --> 00:10:21.559
An alleged affair
by celebrity actor Kuryu Fujiwara.

00:10:22.435 --> 00:10:24.395
Should get plenty of attention, no?

00:10:27.898 --> 00:10:30.526
KURYU FUJIWARA DRANK
AND CHEATED WITH AN UNDERAGE GIRL

00:10:40.035 --> 00:10:41.370
This is fine.

00:10:47.835 --> 00:10:50.337
