00:16:49.321 --> 00:16:51.782
You did more than enough
to get things going.

00:16:52.783 --> 00:16:53.700
I'm sorry.

00:16:58.163 --> 00:16:59.123
Do we let Fujiwara…

00:17:03.502 --> 00:17:04.962
I'll tell him myself.

00:17:11.135 --> 00:17:13.554
Sorry to call you here all of a sudden.

00:17:13.637 --> 00:17:14.763
It's fine.

00:17:14.847 --> 00:17:17.599
It's a shame about that online drama.

00:17:17.683 --> 00:17:20.227
-Your comeback was so close.
-What?

00:17:22.062 --> 00:17:23.647
You haven't heard?

00:17:29.486 --> 00:17:31.071
You've made the wrong decision.

00:17:32.573 --> 00:17:34.658
But I'll give you a chance.

00:17:47.462 --> 00:17:49.131
It's not too late for you.

00:17:50.090 --> 00:17:54.928
I can guarantee you a comeback
and turn you into a star.

00:17:57.806 --> 00:18:02.686
I wonder if Ioka
could manage the same thing.

00:18:08.150 --> 00:18:11.612
EXCLUSIVITY CONTRACT

00:18:31.298 --> 00:18:34.092
THE WRITER OF RIKO'S ARTICLE
CAME TO THE HOSPITAL.

00:18:34.176 --> 00:18:37.554
HE MIGHT BE CONNECTED
TO KODAMA PRODUCTIONS.

00:18:37.638 --> 00:18:40.974
FREELANCE JOURNALIST, YASUO KONDO

00:18:44.561 --> 00:18:46.271
ACTRESS YURI HARA
SUICIDE

00:18:46.355 --> 00:18:48.273
YASUO KONDO, FREELANCE JOURNALIST

00:19:16.677 --> 00:19:18.720
Excuse me, you can't just--

00:19:18.804 --> 00:19:20.013
Ioka.

00:19:20.097 --> 00:19:21.974
What is this? How rude of you--

00:19:22.057 --> 00:19:24.685
It was you. First Yuri and now this.

00:19:25.352 --> 00:19:26.436
What are you on about?

00:19:26.520 --> 00:19:30.065
Riko Hirata tried to commit suicide.
Thankfully, she managed to survive.

00:19:30.774 --> 00:19:33.402
Who? I'm afraid
I've never heard that name.

00:19:34.486 --> 00:19:38.031
Ms. Riko tried to go public
about being assaulted by Aso.

00:19:38.115 --> 00:19:41.743
But then an article defaming her came out.
That was your doing, wasn't it?

00:19:41.827 --> 00:19:43.537
Do you have any proof of that?

00:19:44.621 --> 00:19:45.872
Yasuo Kondo.

00:19:46.623 --> 00:19:47.833
I could never forget.

00:19:48.750 --> 00:19:51.545
That's the reporter who wrote
an article about Yuri Hara,

00:19:51.628 --> 00:19:54.006
after her suicide four year ago.

00:19:55.299 --> 00:19:57.259
He made it seem like her suicide

00:19:57.342 --> 00:19:59.803
was caused by financial disputes
with her father.

00:20:01.138 --> 00:20:03.640
You orchestrated that too, didn't you?

00:20:04.349 --> 00:20:07.978
If people knew that work-related issues
might have caused her suicide,

00:20:08.061 --> 00:20:12.274
it would be seen as a management failure
and damage the agency's reputation!

00:20:14.026 --> 00:20:15.444
Are you done yet?

00:20:17.738 --> 00:20:20.866
I don't have time
for your speculative nonsense.

00:20:22.784 --> 00:20:24.536
Do you not feel anything?

00:20:25.537 --> 00:20:27.956
Do you value
your agency's reputation that much?

00:20:28.040 --> 00:20:29.875
You'd sacrifice lives for it?

00:20:29.958 --> 00:20:31.752
You think that's acceptable?

00:20:31.835 --> 00:20:33.712
You're the one sacrificing lives!

00:20:33.795 --> 00:20:34.588
What?

00:20:34.671 --> 00:20:37.341
What did you ever do
for Yuri Hara and Kuryu Fujiwara?

00:20:37.424 --> 00:20:41.636
You failed to provide a suitable stage
for them or to protect them from harm!

00:20:41.720 --> 00:20:43.138
On the contrary,

00:20:43.221 --> 00:20:46.433
they both lost their future
because they were involved with you.

00:20:47.476 --> 00:20:50.812
And you dare speak to me of management?

00:20:54.608 --> 00:20:57.903
Kuryu learned his lesson the hard way.

00:21:00.155 --> 00:21:01.948
I talked to him just now.

00:21:02.741 --> 00:21:03.867
With Kuryu?

00:21:04.576 --> 00:21:06.453
If he returns to us,

00:21:06.536 --> 00:21:09.915
I promised to get him lead roles
in at least two TV dramas per year,

00:21:09.998 --> 00:21:11.625
as well as four ad contracts.

00:21:11.708 --> 00:21:16.505
And earnings upwards of 200 million yen
in the first year alone.

00:21:16.588 --> 00:21:19.091
You sold him out to a weekly magazine!

00:21:19.174 --> 00:21:21.510
-And now you--
-The choice lies with Kuryu.

00:21:24.930 --> 00:21:27.641
I'm curious what choice he'll make.

00:21:28.892 --> 00:21:30.227
Aren't you?

00:21:43.115 --> 00:21:44.908
EXCLUSIVITY CONTRACT

00:22:24.656 --> 00:22:27.742
Please leave a message after the beep.

00:22:31.246 --> 00:22:32.706
Hey, Kuryu?

00:22:33.456 --> 00:22:34.958
I need to talk to you.

00:22:35.917 --> 00:22:37.377
Can you call me back?

00:23:09.117 --> 00:23:10.327
Ninomiya?

