00:23:35.560 --> 00:23:36.811
She's fine.

00:23:37.646 --> 00:23:38.563
I see.

00:23:57.207 --> 00:24:00.752
Besides your sister,
Aso assaulted others too.

00:24:07.884 --> 00:24:10.762
I went and talked to a couple of them.

00:24:12.806 --> 00:24:13.640
What?

00:24:15.058 --> 00:24:20.063
They saw your sister's post
and found the courage to speak out too.

00:24:23.400 --> 00:24:25.944
If multiple people give their testimony,

00:24:26.027 --> 00:24:28.405
his agency can't just
dismiss it all as lies.

00:24:30.907 --> 00:24:31.866
But why?

00:24:34.286 --> 00:24:36.371
If I hadn't given up on the article…

00:24:38.707 --> 00:24:40.458
this wouldn't have happened to her.

00:24:44.212 --> 00:24:46.298
I'm really sorry.

00:24:56.808 --> 00:24:57.767
Kanade…

